You're a friend on mine.

40:19.080 --> 40:20.400
How about we go
and join the men?

40:20.520 --> 40:26.320
[laughter]

40:26.440 --> 40:29.000
That's quite a good haul.

40:29.120 --> 40:29.880
Isn't it?

40:32.640 --> 40:36.360
Ah, you shouldn't beflushing that about, you know?

