40:41.800 --> 40:42.720
A hooker.

40:42.840 --> 40:44.640
[laughter]

40:44.760 --> 40:46.080
[music playing]

40:46.200 --> 40:47.960
Oh, not this bloody racket.

40:48.080 --> 40:49.160
I like it.

40:49.280 --> 40:50.320
The games are over.

40:50.440 --> 40:52.760
And by Christ,
they had their uses.

40:52.880 --> 40:53.800
To the games.

40:53.920 --> 40:54.880
Bring on the footie!

40:55.000 --> 40:55.880
ALL: The footie!

40:56.000 --> 40:57.840
[cheering]

40:57.960 --> 41:00.320
[laughter]

41:03.400 --> 41:05.240
It's just like old times.

41:05.360 --> 41:06.240
Isn't it?

41:12.800 --> 41:13.640
What was the party for?

41:16.840 --> 41:19.400
Ted's shifted house.

41:19.520 --> 41:21.200
MIKE: Just after
that job at the pub.

41:21.320 --> 41:23.920
Well, he was sitting
there the whole time.

41:24.040 --> 41:25.120
It's a nice place he's got.

41:25.240 --> 41:26.800
You call that information?

41:26.920 --> 41:28.600
I'm paying for a
bit more than that.

41:29.680 --> 41:31.720
I would never turn on Ted--

41:31.840 --> 41:33.240
not ever.

41:33.360 --> 41:36.640
You will-- eventually.

41:36.760 --> 41:38.840
You were meant to
get shot of them!

41:38.960 --> 41:40.240
You're better than them!

41:40.360 --> 41:42.920
I said I'd get you a
new place, and I did.

41:43.040 --> 41:44.440
And you might be in
charge of this house,

41:44.560 --> 41:47.680
but you don't tell me
how to run my gang.

41:47.800 --> 41:49.760
You're my husband, and
I'd do anything for you.

41:49.880 --> 41:50.680
You know that.

41:50.800 --> 41:52.000
You mark my words--

41:52.120 --> 41:53.640
Lefty Munroe will not
thank you for this.

41:53.760 --> 41:54.920
Oh, you think I
don't know that?

42:00.280 --> 42:04.080
They're still good blokes.

42:04.200 --> 42:05.400
And I showed them who's boss.

42:09.280 --> 42:10.040
You did.

42:13.240 --> 42:15.480
I know something else thatmight need a bit of seeing to.

42:20.400 --> 42:21.160
[clattering]

