[MUSIC - STEVE ALEEN, "JOIN TOGETHER"]

42:39.600 --> 42:45.160
We've got to join togetherlet our laughter fill the air.

42:45.280 --> 42:49.080
It's time for every race andcreed to throw away their

42:49.200 --> 42:50.720
every care.

42:50.840 --> 42:56.280
Let sport unite us as one inthe spirit of the Lord above.

42:56.400 --> 43:00.760
